Summary: Reported to cause phenylketonuria, as recorded in ClinVar by three different genetic testing groups (Emory Genetics Lab, Counsyl, and Partners LMM): http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/clinvar/RCV000150075/  This effect seems to be well-supported in literature, e.g. Daniele et al 2007 (PMID: 17096675) report this variant accounting for 11.6% of disease-causing variants in patients studied in Southern Italy.
